&lt;td width="50%"&gt;
&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2011-2014/2011/Msg/VEP-523.htm"&gt;Mensagem de veto&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2011-2014/2011/Lei/L12527.htm#art47"&gt;Vigência&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width="50%"&gt;
&lt;p align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt; &lt;span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;"&gt; &lt;span&gt;Regula o acesso a informações previsto no inciso XXXIII do art. 5&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;sup&gt;o&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, no inciso II do § 3&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;sup&gt;o&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt; do art. 37 e no § 2&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;sup&gt;o&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt; do art. 216 da Constituição Federal; altera a Lei n&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;sup&gt;o&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 8.112, de 11 de dezembro de 1990; revoga a Lei n&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;sup&gt;o&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 11.111, de 5 de maio de 2005, e dispositivos da Lei n&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;sup&gt;o&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 8.159, de 8 de janeiro de 1991; e dá outras providências.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

